License: UNKNOWN
Description: 
        Lightflow
        ---------
        
        Lightflow is a lightweight, distributed workflow system.
        
        It is based on a directed acyclic graph structure, with tasks as nodes and arbitrary data
        flowing between tasks.
        
        
